						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1548 (1626 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Records an endowment probably of land by Aḻagiyaśīyaṉ, the <hi rend="italic">Śrīkāriyam</hi> officer of Tirumaṅgai-Āḻvār and refers to the latter's <hi rend="bold">Divyaprabandham.</hi> The details of the date viz., <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1547, Kshaya, Kārttigai 15, Vṛiśchika śu. 7, Thursday, Sadayam</hi> correspond to <hi rend="bold">1626, A.D., November 16, Thursday; the day of the month is however 17 and not 15; 01; ·75. The Śaka year quoted is wrong for 1548.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
